//
// ## DIY Backends (S3, GCS, Azure, Local)
//
// "DIY" (Do-It-Yourself) backends are self-managed state storage solutions where you
// control the infrastructure. These include:
//   - AWS S3 buckets
//   - S3-compatible storage (Cloudflare R2, MinIO)
//   - Google Cloud Storage (GCS)
//   - Azure Blob Storage
//   - Local filesystem
